{
  "1860320": {
    "name": "Polygon of Reality",
    "steam_appid": 1860320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一片漆黑中，人们不禁会怀疑自己是否是一个人。也许有一天，关了灯，人们会听到身后传来非人类的呼吸声。还记得儿时的噩梦吗？未知总是让我们感到害怕。也许在这里，你会揭开你曾如此恐惧的神秘面纱。潜入另一个拥有秘密和生物的空间。请继续前进，停下来可能意味着永远被困在这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要进入深埋地下的建筑群，揭开多年前这里发生的一切，以及很久以前被无名生物从你记忆中抹去的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当地生物的外表可能具有欺骗性；看起来最无害的生物可能会变成嗜血的杀手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 你不敢停车，也不敢掉头。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/ea1f327942cee4461f0d695266b7992a.poster.avif?t=1729788971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/ea1f327942cee4461f0d695266b7992a.webm?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/ea1f327942cee4461f0d695266b7992a.mp4?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 功能：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据玩家的选择，游戏地点和玩法会发生巨大变化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家往往需要多次尝试才能在挑战中生存下来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有多个结局，完全取决于玩家的选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会遇到各种各样的生物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种生物都有自己独特的特点，玩家必须考虑到这些特点才能确保自己的生存。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 从敌对生物手中逃脱！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/98d2db17ee6d631598826b9da5ab80fb.poster.avif?t=1729788971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/98d2db17ee6d631598826b9da5ab80fb.webm?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/98d2db17ee6d631598826b9da5ab80fb.mp4?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃离敌对生物！您会遇到各种各样的生物，每种生物都需要采取不同的行动才能生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些可以通过逃跑逃脱，有些则只能通过躲藏来躲避。有些生物可能需要采取特定行动才能拯救你的生命，你也可以尝试打败它们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >或者您可以尝试打败它们！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/21f5d8fcd4b12a4ebdef72b2000ce879.poster.avif?t=1729788971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/21f5d8fcd4b12a4ebdef72b2000ce879.webm?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/21f5d8fcd4b12a4ebdef72b2000ce879.mp4?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，在该地点找到的某些物品可以用来阻止某些生物。不过要小心，一个错误可能会激怒生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 搜索档案文件和物品，以求生存并揭开多年前这里发生的一切。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/6bcf0433937eb8e4151c5f31679fbb8c.poster.avif?t=1729788971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/6bcf0433937eb8e4151c5f31679fbb8c.webm?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/6bcf0433937eb8e4151c5f31679fbb8c.mp4?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了了解这里的历史，档案文件还可能揭示对抗生物的方法。此外，一定要收集所有找到的物品，因为它们可能会救你一命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/fca23a6969f77c330bfa5f4fe65675be.poster.avif?t=1729788971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/fca23a6969f77c330bfa5f4fe65675be.webm?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860320/extras/fca23a6969f77c330bfa5f4fe65675be.mp4?t=1729788971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
